T02TD3284E:29b-1: krishna ya m'a ri s'a dha nam /
T02TD3284E:29b-3: gshin rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3284E:29b-4: dpa' bo thod pa'i phreng ldan zhing //
T02TD3284E:30a-1: sogs kyis brgyan bzhin sgyur ba'i //
T02TD3284E:30a-2: gshin rje mthar mdzad mgon btud nas //
T02TD3284E:30a-3: de yi sgrub thabs bri bar bya //
T02TD3284E:30a-4: bde ba'i stan la legs gnas la //
T02TD3284E:30a-5: snying ga'i nyi mar h'um gzugs dgod //
T02TD3284E:30a-6: de byung mchod pa'i khyad par gyis //
T02TD3284E:30a-7: rje bo gus pas yang dag mchod//
T02TD3284E:30a-8: mdun phyogs su ni sdig la sogs //
T02TD3284E:30a-9: bshags pa la sogs de la bya //
T02TD3284E:30a-10: de nyid du ni 'jig rten kun //
T02TD3284E:30a-11: rang bzhin med par skad cig blta //
T02TD3284E:30a-12: snying sa bon bskyed phyag mtshan las //
T02TD3284E:30a-13: bzhengs par padmar brkyang bskum zhabs //
T02TD3284E:30a-14: khro gnyer sdud pa 'jigs pa'i zhal //
T02TD3284E:30a-15: smin ma smar ser ba gyen //
T02TD3284E:30a-16: zhal gsum ljags ni 'dril bar mdzad //
T02TD3284E:30a-17: 'jigs pa'i mche ba gcum [?] par gtsigs //
T02TD3284E:30a-18: spyan mig dmar zhing gsus pa che //
T02TD3284E:30a-19: mthing nag gzhon nu sdug po'i 'od //
T02TD3284E:30a-20: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dbus gnas pa //
T02TD3284E:30a-21: mgo bo'i rus pas brgyan pa ste //
T02TD3284E:30a-22: bong thung stag lpags sham thabs can //
T02TD3284E:30a-23: dregs pa thams cad 'joms par mdzad //
T02TD3284E:30a-24: nyi ma'i 'od ldan gzi brjid che //
T02TD3284E:30a-25: sa 'og ma lus rnams kyis mchod //
T02TD3284E:30a-27: dus mtha'i me dang mtshungs pa yin //
T02TD3284E:30a-28: rdo rje ral gri dbyug gdug pa'i //
T02TD3284E:30a-29: chu gri mdung dang zhags pa bsnams //
T02TD3284E:30a-30: g-yas dang g-yon gyi phyag gis ni //
T02TD3284E:30a-31: rnam gsal bsnams pa lha rdzas drug / khro ldan 'jigs pa shin tu drag / gshin rje gshed po bdud rnams 'joms //
T02TD3284E:30a-32: h'um sgras mgrin pa gang bar ni //
T02TD3284E:30a-33: bsgom par bya ba'i nga rgyal des //
T02TD3284E:30a-34: stong nyid snying rje'i snying 'od kyis /
T02TD3284E:30a-37: mdun yul bzhugs la legs mchod de //
T02TD3284E:30a-38: rang rnams gcig tu brjod bya ba //
T02TD3284E:30a-40: legs par spyan 'dren rab zhugs dang //
T02TD3284E:30a-41: bcing dang ma nyes bya ba dag nyid la //
T02TD3284E:30a-42: bsam gtan mchod pas mchod bya ba //
T02TD3284E:30a-43: legs bstod de nas bsngags bzlas la //
T02TD3284E:30a-44: dge ba yongs su bsngo byas te //
T02TD3284E:30a-45: lha yi rnal 'byor gyis langs la //
T02TD3284E:30a-46: gcig tu snying rje'i yid kyis rgyu //
T02TD3284E:30a-47: de ltar nyi ma re byas pas //
T02TD3284E:30a-48: dngos grub thob pa'i rgyu mtshan can //
T02TD3284E:30a-49: brjod pa'i dngos grub bsgrub par bya //
T02TD3284E:30a-50: las mchog kha tshar ba yis kyang //
T02TD3284E:30b-0: @30b las dang rjes mthun sku yin te //
T02TD3284E:30b-1: shin tu rgyas 'dir ma brjod pa //
T02TD3284E:30b-2: de yang bla ma'i gdams ngag dang //
T02TD3284E:30b-4: brtson pas shes bya blo ldan gyis //
T02TD3284E:30b-6: gtor ma gtang ba'i sbyor ba ni //
T02TD3284E:30b-7: thun bzhi la ni mchog tu bya //
T02TD3284E:30b-9: aom hr'i:sht'i:bi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3284E:30b-10: bla ma'i bzhed pa'i cho ga bzhin du legs rtogs nas //
T02TD3284E:30b-11: sgrub thabs bdag gis bkod las byung ba'i bsod nams kyis //
T02TD3284E:30b-12: myur du mngon par 'dod pa'i 'bras bu 'thob byed pa'i //
T02TD3284E:30b-13: sa yi phun tshogs thams cad 'jig rten la 'dir shog / gshin rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD3284E:30b-15: // / pandi ta aa bha ya'i zhal snga nas dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
